<!-- HERO -->
<section id="home" class="hero">
<div class="overlay">
<div class="container text-center">
<h1 class="display-4 fw-bold">Nyawit Raharja</h1>
<p>Mendedikasikan hidup untuk kelapa sawit berkelanjutan</p>
<button class="btn btn-warning btn-lg mt-3" onclick="scrollAbout()">Kenali Saya</button>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section id="about" class="py-5 text-center">
<div class="container">
<h2 class="section-title mb-4">Siapa Nyawit Raharja?</h2>
<p class="col-md-8 mx-auto">
Petani kelapa sawit berpengalaman lebih dari 20 tahun di Sumatera. 
Menerapkan teknik modern ramah lingkungan dan menghasilkan TBS kualitas premium.
</p>

<div class="row mt-4">
<div class="col"><h3>50+</h3><p>Hektar Lahan</p></div>
<div class="col"><h3>100%</h3><p>Organik Parsial</p></div>
<div class="col"><h3>25 Th</h3><p>Pengalaman</p></div>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<!-- PANEN -->
<section id="panen" class="py-5 bg-light text-center">
<div class="container">
<h2 class="section-title mb-4">Dokumentasi & Hasil Panen</h2>

<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-4">
<div class="card shadow">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1509316975850-ff9c5deb0cd9" class="card-img-top">
<div class="card-body">
<h5>Pembibitan Unggul</h5>
<p>Bibit DxP berkualitas tinggi.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="col-md-4">
<div class="card shadow">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1599058918144-1ffabb6ab9a0" class="card-img-top">
<div class="card-body">
<h5>Pemeliharaan Intensif</h5>
<p>Pemupukan tepat & kontrol gulma.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="col-md-4">
<div class="card shadow">
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1587049352846-4a222e784d38" class="card-img-top">
<div class="card-body">
<h5>Panen Raya</h5>
<p>TBS segar dengan rendemen tinggi.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<!-- KONTAK -->
<section id="kontak" class="py-5 text-center">
<div class="container">
<h2 class="section-title mb-4">Hubungi Nyawit</h2>

<div class="col-md-8 mx-auto">
<form onsubmit="kirimPesan(event)">
<input class="form-control mb-3" placeholder="Nama Lengkap" required>
<input type="email" class="form-control mb-3" placeholder="Email" required>
<textarea class="form-control mb-3" placeholder="Pesan"></textarea>
<button class="btn btn-warning w-100">Kirim Pesan</button>
</form>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<footer class="footer text-center p-4">
<p>© 2026 Portofolio Nyawit Raharja. Semua Hak Dilindungi.</p>
